{% if publisher.event.slug %}
	{% set eventID = publisher.event.slug %}
{% else %}
	{% set eventID = publisher.event.id %}
{% endif %}
<div style="background-color:#f5f2e8; padding:20px 0;">
    <div id="logo-email" style="background-color:#3e444c; width:590px; margin-left:auto; margin-right:auto; padding-left:10px; line-height:50px;">
        <a style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none; font-family: Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif; font-size:20px; padding-left:8px;" href="{{ url('homepage') }}">üç∫ Live Beer Feed</a>
    </div>
	<div id="cont-mail" style=" width:600px; height:auto; margin-right:auto;	margin-left:auto;	background-color:#2e3338; padding-top:20px;">
        <div id="bonjour-email" style="font-family: Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif; margin-left:20px; font-size:20px;	color:#c8c8c8; width:300px; font-weight:500;">Hi {{ publisher.name }},</div>
        <div class="txt-email" style="font-family: Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;	margin-left:20px;	font-size:14px;	color:#c8c8c8;	width:550px; line-height:22px;">
			<p>It looks like you have not submitted your beers (and ciders) to the {{ publisher.event.name }} tap list yet. Do not hesitate to do it as soon as possible in order to allow the event's organizer to communicate the most complete tap list to the visitors.</p>
			<p>If you have any questions, feel free to email me at <a href="mailto:robin@livebeerfeed.com" style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none;">robin@livebeerfeed.com</a>.</p> 
			<p>You can use the following URL to log into your brewery portal:<br />
			<a href="{{ url('brewery_portal',{'eventID': eventID}) }}" style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none;">{{ url('brewery_portal',{'eventID': eventID}) }}</a></p> 
	        <p>As a reminder, your access code is:</p>
			<div id="box-commentaire" style="margin-top:20px;	margin-left:15px;	width:500px;	height:auto;	padding:15px; background-color:#1c1e22;	 border: 1px solid #0c0d0e; border-radius:4px; margin-bottom:20px;">{{ publisher.accessKey }}</div>
			<p>The {{ publisher.event.name }} tap list is available at the following URL:<br />
			<a href="{{ url('taplist',{'eventID': eventID}) }}" style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none;">{{ url('taplist',{'eventID': eventID}) }}</a></p> 			
			<p>Cheers,<br />Robin from <a href="{{ url('homepage') }}" style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none;">Live Beer Feed</a></p>
     	</div>
        
		<div id="footer-email" style="height:30px;	margin-top:10px; padding-bottom:10px; font-family: Helvetica,Verdana,sans-serif;	font-size:10px;	color:#999999;	text-align:center;">
	        <div id="footer-sep-email" style="margin-top:20px;	width:500px;	height:1px;	background-color:#c8c8c8;	margin-right:auto;	margin-left:auto;"></div>    
			<p>If you have any questions about Live Beer Feed, feel free to email me at <a href="mailto:robin@livebeerfeed.com" style="color:#dddddd; text-decoration:none;">robin@livebeerfeed.com</a>.</p>
     	</div>
    </div>
</div>